node.title: This week on "Face the Nation with Margaret Brennan," January 30, 2022
node.description: Senator Lindsey Graham, Ukrainian Ambassador to the U.S. Oksana Markarova and more appear on "Face the Nation with Margaret Brennan" on Sunday.
